{"tid":1637208,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 想罷工搞得成嘅同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-10-08T02:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:40:44.000Z","uid":279478,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6110757c56974af709162fc0ab13125af59bed95","tid":1637208,"uid":279478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:16:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">罷工</span></span>，一向都係一條打唔響<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">對政府最有威脅</span></span>嘅戰線。香港人最鍾意就係返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要大家長期罷工幾乎無可能，尤其85罷工之後，大家都好似放棄左罷工呢條戰線咁。<br />\n<br />\n但我仍然覺得可以開拓依條戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國泰內部審查</span></span>愈來愈嚴重，好多發表過支持示威者既人都相繼被炒，係依個環境下，絕對係罷工既重要時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人依家輸得只剩下錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地有無可能<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用眾籌方式成立罷工基金</span></span>經濟上支持國泰員工罷工？當然行政細節上我都無咩概念要點做，但依條戰線一打響，絕對對一d有大量黃絲既紅色企業有好大威脅。<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果國泰員工罷工搞得成，一定會號召到更多人罷工。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">國泰成功 下一站就係狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家參考下2013年嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">葵涌貨櫃碼頭罷工潮</span></span>都做過類似嘅野：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">//</span>何偉航呼籲巿民踴躍捐助罷工基金，其中立法會議員余若薇、梁國雄、何秀蘭、毛孟靜及時事節目主時人鄭經翰，昨亦到場捐款數千至12,000元以示支持。同時，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">工會昨正式成立「罷工基金管理委員會」</span></span>，成員包括教協主席馮偉華、立法會議員毛孟靜及大律師黃瑞紅。基金計劃明日向每名罷工的工會會員派發300元津貼。<span style=\"color: red;\">//</span><br />\n<br />\n當年嘅規模都唔細<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t14enPb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft14enPb.png&h=18115140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130401/18213526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130401%2F18213526&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIpHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=d7f1fc52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130401%2F18213526&h=e69fcffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130401/18213526</a><br />\n<br />\n當年民意關注度不足 但大家諗下我地宜家有超過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">200萬嘅民意 </span></span>眾籌成立罷工基金一定唔係問題！<br />\n<br />\n再加上國泰員工唔係固定返星期一至五朝九晚六嘅 一眾鍾意返工嘅香港人放工同放假都可以去支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n我地 一個都不能少了</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e3ecebcd276ab18d3364e2ee0d5cf98bc5396b0","tid":1637208,"uid":279478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:16:58.000Z","msg":"P牌自己推唔起 幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c58c8f27f66e404bba3c639ad68e092975c358","tid":1637208,"uid":205347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:29:20.000Z","msg":"係時候要好好咁組織一次三罷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636131</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"31a03274718afd15343dd7cab439eb7f6cf22269","tid":1637208,"uid":192736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"451a456ef9ea6864178b055f78f7bfb3cd16e4fb","tid":1637208,"uid":279478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8957144f1442fec